					</div>
					<div class="faq-item">
						<h3>How active is the community?</h3>
						<p>Members typically respond within 24 hours. Quality conversations happen daily across multiple domains and specialties.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="faq-item">
						<h3>What happens after approval?</h3>
						<p>You'll receive an invitation to our private community platform with guidelines, introductions, and access to ongoing discussions.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="faq-item">
						<h3>Can I promote my services?</h3>
						<p>No. This is a peer support community, not a marketplace. Promotional content results in immediate removal.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="faq-item">
						<h3>How do you maintain quality?</h3>
						<p>Through careful vetting, active moderation, and a culture that prioritizes helpful, actionable contributions over self-promotion.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- CTA Section -->
		<section class="cta-section">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="cta-content">
					<h2>Ready to connect with exceptional professionals?</h2>
					<p>Applications are reviewed weekly. We maintain excellence by remaining highly selective.</p>
					<a href="mailto:hello@example.com?subject=Application%20to%20Join%20Professional%20Community&body=Hi%2C%0A%0AI%27d%20like%20to%20apply%20to%20join%20your%20exclusive%20professional%20community.%0A%0AHere%27s%20a%20bit%20about%20me%3A%0A%0A-%20Current%20Role%3A%20%0A-%20Company%3A%20%0A-%20Years%20of%20Experience%3A%20%0A-%20Domain%20Expertise%3A%20%0A-%20What%20value%20I%27d%20bring%3A%20%0A-%20LinkedIn%20Profile%3A%20%0A%0AThanks%21" class="btn-primary large">Apply to Join</a>
